paragraph.text:
Any cash equalization payment received by the Secretary under this subsection shall be deposited into the fund established by 

                Public Law 90–171
               (commonly known as the Sisk Act; 
                16 U.S.C. 484a
              ). The payment shall be available to the Secretary for expenditure, without further appropriation and until expended, for the acquisition of land or interests in land for addition to the National Forest System.
